commit.title: [dune] Update dune version to support "watch" continuous build mode.
commit.message:
[dune] Update dune version to support "watch" continuous build mode.

`make -f Makefile.dune watch` will now watch for files changes
and rebuild what is needed.

This feature requires `fswatch` or `inotifywait`.
